creatureBayingGourmetMale.name: Baying Gourmet
creatureBayingGourmetMale.appDesc: You are covered in a thick layer of fur. Your face is that of large manacing wolf. You really look like a monster from the Abyss!

creatureBayingGourmetFemale.name: Baying Gourmet
creatureBayingGourmetFemale.appDesc: You are covered in a thick layer of fur. Your face is that of large manacing wolf. You really look like a monster from the Abyss!

creatureDragonMale.name: Dragon
creatureDragonMale.appDesc: Your scaly hide and horns combined with the reptilian wings can only mean one thing. You look like a fearsome dragon!

creatureDragonFemale.name: Dragon
creatureDragonFemale.appDesc: Your scaly hide and horns combined with the reptilian wings can only mean one thing. You look like a fearsome dragon!

companions.name: Maru
companions.appDesc: Your skin is extremely soft and bruises easily. Any material rougher than silk feels uncomfortable on it now.

companions.name: Lily
companions.appDesc: You have particularly long eyelashes, and your legs seem long compared to your height. Your pupils are heart-shaped.

companions.name: Khemia
companions.appDesc: You have blue spiral tattoos through the length of both arms, and your hands are calloused from over a decade of hard work. Your voice seems to draw more attention than it used to before switching bodies.

companions.name: Cherry
companions.appDesc: Your body feels low on energy often, and you feel like you need more sleep than you used to.

companions.name: Cloud
companions.appDesc: Your sight is pretty good, and you can focus on distant objects more easily. Your smile seems to easily earn people's trust.

companions.name: Saeko
companions.appDesc: Your sight is pretty bad without glasses and your eyebrows are relatively thin.

relics.name: Starlit Conquest Activated
relics.desc: The starlit conquest mecha in all its glory. It has been activated by the power of the sun and is ready for use!
